      "date": "2011-10-03 17:58:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Abandoned\n\nBy including this test in sanity.sh a hard dependency between lustre and lustre-tar is enforced. \n\nThis is not desirable.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
