      "date": "2012-07-28 07:00:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64, CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e360194e-d87f-11e1-9e3b-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
