        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2012-07-28 14:08:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5e0e55c6-d8bb-11e1-9e3b-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
